\n但detailed啲就呢啲transmitters eg Acetylcholine, dopamine 會由一條神經線傳到另一條神經線，去到目標既cells，令佢有動作<br />\n所以有時帕金順症（即係手震）就係腦退化至準備不足的dopamine 隻手就唔知要佢做啲咩，收唔到signal所以手震震<br />\n而好多毒品就係令啲transmitter更多 令個人感受更多 感官放大 好high<br />\n唔明再問我 唔使神經學家 有讀bio就識"},{"pid":"c81e456c96746e6f1bf2e2cc3259df8c0ada86ee","tid":1567189,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3edf5bc99701502ee3dfcf2970ee5ebe475a2fbe","tid":1567189,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceba985ab1737174a6a5576218b1a2e9e5a4d02d","tid":1567189,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e59b27f9945c418734feb695017bd40eceff47ff","tid":1567189,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:28:52.000Z","msg":"你個腦唔係諗出拳 係叫個腦模擬自己出拳<br />\n<br />\n所以 從科學定 日常生活黎講， 想做 同 做 係有分別"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:32:30.000Z","msg":"有一部大腦控制嘅機器人 然後諗住模擬出拳 咁架機器人會唔會出拳？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"然後[你]諗住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:49:35.000Z","msg":"視乎你點寫個機械人既program<br />\n<br />\n你可以寫到佢detect 你有諗緊模擬舉起拳頭既時候 舉起 隻腳<br />\n<br />\nbtw 腦入面既signal 科學家都仲未好仔細咁pinpoint 到 例如你諗住一樣事物個陣你個腦會有幾部份會有好多signal 邊部份有signal 代表諗緊咩事物 暫時未完全做到<br />\n<br />\n反而好大概既brain mapping 就有 例如 人有情緒 係咩部份 同堆人做緊決定個陣係用前額葉 等等<br />\n<br />\n所以有學識既賊攞桿打劫 會打前額 條友即刻唔知要做咩<br />\n<br />\nbtw 唔推了 要留位俾行動post"},{"pid":"5f23ab1dc47a6186aa8b1ebe446289558c38de8b","tid":1567189,"uid":314619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:02:20.000Z","msg":"岩岩只係儱統咁講 <br />\nSignal =/= neurotransmitters<br />\n中間係涉及voltage（即係signal係靠正負電子傳送先可以咁快）但當電傳到synapse（兩條神經線中間嘅gap) 就會變成neurotransmitters以確保啲signal只係one-way<br />\n所以點解中學用電電青蛙神經線會令佢陏<br />\n呢樣野叫membrane potential <a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Membrane_potential\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMembrane_potential&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=e3d1a822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Membrane_potential</a><br />\n好Fundamental 既 biology"},{"pid":"131a847fa4cb289538f0baefc18e072388817bd0","tid":1567189,"uid":314619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62915251950d986f29d8ae1497db9f7e831c89c","tid":1567189,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c13c846e95dd70b882f0d58e8c764d9c2b6f686","tid":1567189,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12b4c5e958ac308f50686e3e0ebdbde03078deaa","tid":1567189,"uid":314619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">念頭 idea 係 有做某件事既諗法但冇具體地想過達到既方法<br />\n行動 action 係有具體既計劃planning/方法去達到某件事<br />\n企圖就介乎兩者之間 有達到既目的同planing 只差action<br />\nHi I thought this was so easy 你個degree係咪買返黎</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"大字講野有道理啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇清楚我條問題先啦<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">P牌狗</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:05:11.000Z","msg":"咁而家明未也？😉"},{"pid":"32b880de9d6ad23fdfb7f623e8a01e24e3f9702d","tid":1567189,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fd7b2b7ceb926f76c97637a3bcc912326b5d22","tid":1567189,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"幾有趣嘅問題"},{"pid":"1bf505ba566aef1ac4fa88